        {
            "title": "捐糞有錢收︱深圳科技公司每次津貼¥300  每月最多達¥6600",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"深圳科技公司接受已登記人士捐糞，每次津貼¥300。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f9743928cb8988ed378d6d2dabdfc640/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021913030322921.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">深圳科技公司接受已登記人士捐糞，每次津貼¥300。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>有無想過，大便可以「點糞成金」。近日，深圳一間叫「未知君」的生物公司，招募志願者捐糞便。合格捐贈者每次可獲300元（人民幣‧下同）補貼，最高月入高達6600元。事件即引起網友關注。\n\n</p>\n<p>深圳新聞網報道，該公司相關負責人表示，志願者需要線上完成問卷調查，然後線下面試體檢。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"志願者捐糞前要先登記再做檢查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/75431f5e10ca075b4417d5d2114831f2/2025-02/101_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        志願者捐糞前要先登記再做檢查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"每次捐糞可獲300元人民幣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a4ff53a73ac971038d4ee131d6d0cfe0/2025-02/103_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        每次捐糞可獲300元人民幣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>用於研究胃腸道疾病</h2>\n<p>收集大便後，經過處理的菌液樣本將用於研究胃腸道疾病治療。志願者需簽知情書。<br/>\n<br/>\n網上流出影片見，已有不少志願者參與捐贈，工作人員則進行歸檔、分類的工作。<br/>\n<br/>\n對此大便能廢物利用，網民紛紛表示想報名，「心動了」、「可以包郵嗎，我寄過去」、「願意為科研出力」。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053659/即時-中國-捐糞有錢收︱深圳科技公司每次津貼¥300-每月最多達¥6600",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 13:11:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "恒生部分香港地產客要求延遲還款 去年不良貸款率增至6.12%",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/8fad7c941259d2a78fa268fe04f1b003/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021912492448423.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>恒生銀行 （011）去年盈利按年增⻑3%至183.79億元，宣布派發第四次中期息3.2元，全年股息合計6.8元，按年增4.6%。\n\n</p>\n<p>值得留意，恒生表示在⾼息環境持續下，部分香港商業房地產客⼾持續有現⾦流壓⼒，由於部分香港房地產客⼾要求延遲還款，截至去年年底不良貸款比率為6.12%，較去年6月底的5.32%進一步上升。\n\n</p><h2>對財務表現無顯著影響</h2>\n<p>不過，該行補充三分之二的貸款均有提供充⾜的抵押品作擔保。無擔保貸款的質量亦保持穩定，其中90%以上屬於投資級別，因此對財務表現並無顯著影響，預期信貸損失提撥按年減少24%。恒生又指，已持續減低內地商業房地產貸款的風險承擔。截⾄去年年底，內地房地產佔比貸款組合⼤約2%\n\n</p>\n<p>恒生去年淨利息收入減少5%至307.84億元；淨利息收益率收窄10個基點至2.2厘。非利息收入上升26%至107.53億元。\n\n</p>\n<p>淨服務費收入亦增加8%至53.16億元，原因是受惠投資服務收入持續表現強勁，當中主要由零售投資基⾦、證券經紀及相關服務增⻑所帶動。\n\n</p>\n<p>恒生績前收報104.1元，跌0.47%。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053657/即時-財經-恒生部分香港地產客要求延遲還款-去年不良貸款率增至6-12",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-19 12:56:30",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "俄烏戰爭｜特朗普疑與澤連斯基「割席」  批基輔不應挑釁",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"特朗普疑與澤連斯基「割席」，批烏克蘭不應開戰。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e6a13a5997e9352e163ded68ffbfce92/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021912391125716.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">特朗普疑與澤連斯基「割席」，批烏克蘭不應開戰。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國與俄羅斯於當地時間18日上午10時30分，在沙特阿拉伯首都利雅德就終結俄烏戰爭展開初步會談。會後，美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，烏克蘭挑起俄烏衝突，導致其領土遭到破壞、千萬人喪生。\n\n</p><h2>說辭對烏藏「敵意」</h2>\n<p>美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）、英國廣播公司（BBC）報道，特朗普又指，烏克蘭應該儘快舉行大選。他先是將烏克蘭和歐洲國家排除在會議之外，然後又發出「敵意」言論，引起歐洲諸國的擔憂。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3430247/%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E5%89%8D%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B11026%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E6%97%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%A4%95-%E6%BE%A4%E9%80%A3%E6%96%AF%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%96%E8%82%85%E6%B8%85%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE\">烏克蘭前總統：10.26大選日前夕 澤連斯基圖肅清反對派</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普與俄羅斯總統普京通話備受關注。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a7561e225fd29b8a04688e8373c5ceb1/2025-02/19022025_041_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普與俄羅斯總統普京通話備受關注。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普斥烏克蘭不應開戰。（美聯社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4a42f4cb71e879d9688f81d3913d700/2025-02/19022025_042_AP.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普斥烏克蘭不應開戰。（美聯社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普斥烏克蘭不應開戰。（美聯社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c8aa6fb794f6af2363969be536272e7/2025-02/19022025_043_AP.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普斥烏克蘭不應開戰。（美聯社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"特朗普促烏克蘭進行大選。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68fac7881bcdc56f68fa55deb8becc18/2025-02/19022025_044_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普促烏克蘭進行大選。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"俄羅斯總統普京。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d276b3898104ea4c1a3b231aa93187d4/2025-02/19022025_045_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        俄羅斯總統普京。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>報道指，特朗普的說辭迎合俄方，使人擔憂美俄雙方將達成一個有利俄羅斯，而不利烏克蘭的和平協議。然而，美國國務卿魯比奧（Marco Rubio）曾作出保證，指美俄達成的協議將對各方公平。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3430221/%E4%BF%84%E7%83%8F%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%88%96%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E6%99%A4%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC-%E4%B8%80%E8%87%89%E4%B8%8D%E5%B1%91%E8%AB%87%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E8%A2%AB%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4\">俄烏戰爭｜特朗普：或月底晤普京 一臉不屑談烏克蘭「被缺席」停火談判</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"美俄就俄烏戰爭舉行會談。（美聯社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77dd3eeb403d4e5b8de55bf6b0820aad/2025-02/19022025_036_AP.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美俄就俄烏戰爭舉行會談。（美聯社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯比奧稱和平協議將對各方公平。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/967fc14fdb3ff041dfb12515617d6c33/2025-02/19022025_037_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯比奧稱和平協議將對各方公平。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯比奧稱和平協議將對各方公平。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8245c45699a699c9d5aa0cea884e324a/2025-02/19022025_038_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯比奧稱和平協議將對各方公平。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c549ccbfd6bac1780e202049ce12a13f/2025-02/19022025_039_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫。（路透社）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6155daddf859aa36e65c33dd8919d06b/2025-02/19022025_040_Reuter.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫。（路透社）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>特朗普於海湖莊園向記者說：「們現在的情況是，烏克蘭還沒有舉行選舉，而且實行了戒嚴。澤連斯基的支持率只有4%，國家也被炸得粉碎。」報道指，澤連斯基的支持率確實有大幅下跌趨勢，但遠遠沒有特朗普說的誇張。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053656/即時-國際-俄烏戰爭-特朗普疑與澤連斯基-割席-批基輔不應挑釁",
